<subSubSection pageId="47" pageNumber="324" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="47.[1454,2660,1871,2610]" pageId="47" pageNumber="324">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1456,1805,2458,2491]" pageId="47" pageNumber="324">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. Threats to Forrest’s Mountain Vole are unknown, and there is no information ofit occurring in protected areas.
</paragraph>
